If you wish that your values will be reloaded each time start PHCtool is starting, just check in the box(es).<br>
PHCtool can be started with the parameter "background". Using this parameter PHCtool will start without a GUI,
reloading your values and quits.<br><br>
This parameter is alse been used by the tray icon to reload your values after you log in.
<br><br>
The settings are stored in a hidden file in your home directory named ".phcstore.phc". Each user on your system
can have its own settings.

